  <p class="lede">Condos and managed apartment buildings near CMU/Suthep with recent rental turnover. The local move: walk in and ask the <strong>juristic office</strong> (นิติบุคคล, usually ground floor) or the apartment <strong>front desk</strong> — they hold keys and owner contacts, and many owners only list with them, not online.</p>
